This skill allows a thief to throw a specially designed dagger
available for purchase at the guild poison shop at an unsuspecting
opponent. As your skills with a dagger increase, you will see your
accuracy and time between throws improve as well. You will find
that if your aim is true, you will be able to hit a target from
several screens away as well. 
The syntax to use this skill is "dthrow <target>".
This skill costs 25 sps.
